properties.Name: ChannelProductSalesPlan
properties.Description: The Sales Plan by Channel for which the associated individual product/service-related budgets are prepared.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: OperatingBudgetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product/Service Operating Budget.

Columns.Name: OperatingBudgetVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Operating Budget Version.

Columns.Name: PlannedChannelProductUnitsSales
Columns.Description:
The planned number of product-related unit sales for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Municipal Bond Sales = n units

Columns.Name: PlannedChannelProductSalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description:
The planned revenue to be derived from product-related unit sales for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Number of Municipal Bond Sales = $1,500M

Columns.Name: ActualChannelProductUnitsSales
Columns.Description:
The actual number of product-related unit sales for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Municipal Bond Sales = n units

Columns.Name: ActualChannelProductSalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description:
The actual revenue derived from product-related unit sales for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Number of Municipal Bond Sales = $1,500M

Columns.Name: PlannedNumberChannelServiceDeliveries
Columns.Description:
The planned number of service-related units of services to be delivered for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Number Of Wire Transfer Transactions = n services deliveries

Columns.Name: PlannedChannelServiceDeliveryRevenueAmount
Columns.Description:
The planned revenue to be derived from service-related unit sales for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Number Of Wire Transfer Transactions = n services deliveries = $200,500 in service fees

Columns.Name: ActualNumberChannelServiceDeliveries
Columns.Description:
The actual number of service-related units of services to be delivered for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Number Of Wire Transfer Transactions = n services deliveries

Columns.Name: ActualChannelServiceDeliveryRevenueAmount
Columns.Description:
The actual revenue derived from service-related unit sales for the associated budget period by channel.

Ex:
Number Of Wire Transfer Transactions = n services deliveries = $200,500 in service fees
